ise befriedigt werden. Dabei deckt er auch im Verborgenen wirksame Netzwerkeffekte in Form ökonomischer und politischer Verflechtungen auf.  afunded by Swiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aOrganizational sociology. 0aSocial sciences. 4aGesellschaft. 4aHomophilie. 4aInstitutionalismus. 4aLogen. 4aMikro-Institution. 4aMythos. 4aMännerbund. 4aNeo-Institutionalismus. 4aNetzwerke. 4aNonprofit. 4aOrganisationssoziologie. 4aResistenz. 4aRitual. 4aService Clubs. 4aSoziologie. 4aStudentenverbindungen. 4aStudierendenvereine. 4aTransparenz. 4aVereinswesen. 4aZeremonie. 4aZünfte. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aCeremony.  aClub.  aGuilds.  aHomophily.  aInstitutionalism.  aLodges.  aMale Association.  aMicro-institution.  aMyth.  aNeo-institutionalism.  aNetworks.  aNonprofit.  aResistance.  aRitual.  aService Clubs.  aSociety.  aSociology of Organizations.  aSociology.  aStudent Associations.  aStudent Relations.  aTransparency.2 aSwiss National Science Foundation (SNSF)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2020z9783111025124oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383765283340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/97838